INSERT INTO tbl_about VALUES("1","Everything began with a dream.","This is a true story about me.","For those who know me and for those who don\'t, I would like to say this is a new beginning in my life.","1616438.jpg","<strong>I was born in Malaysia, educated both in Singapore and Melbourne (Australia) for about 14 years.</strong>\n\nBeing away from my parents at a young tender age, this experience inevitably had trained me to be independent, particularly in the areas of self learning such as goal settings, leadership etc. During my growing up time, my parents were not always around due to work. I envied seeing those friends whose mothers always fetch them to school everyday. I knew my mum would\'ve loved to do that for her children if she\'s given the flexibility in the area of her work. Frankly speaking, this particular childhood memory made a deep impression in my heart.","I thought to myself, in the future, I would like to have a business which not only can bring financial freedom to me, but also allows me to have the opportunity to learn and grow to become a better person to my love ones, as well as to serve and empower ladies in the community. I did not expect this little seed planted in my heart many years ago to come true in 2013 when the Ladies Rock Online was formed.\n\nI love to dream. Since young, I dreamt to have a business which would give me freedom in terms of making money and time. I reckon my dad has played a major role in cultivating the entrepreneurship spirit and lifelong learning attitude in my life. I remember in 2002, while still doing my undergraduate degree in Monash Uni, I had a dream of doing business using the internet. I love to travel and I thought, \"wouldn\'t it be cool to travel with ease while money still rolls into my pocket?\" I want to explore the world, learn different cultures, make new friends around the globe and most importantly, make a positive impact in the community. I want to be able to LIVE N EARN> anywhere and anytime I want. I knew the only way to fulfill this dream was to do something Online. However, I had no clue how and where to get started. Just like what Steve Jobs said : \"If you haven\'t found it yet, keep looking. Don\'t settle. As with all matters of the heart, you\'ll know when you find it\". Hence, I decided to take time to do my research while running my other businesses which include financial planning services business.\n\nMy financial planning business was doing very well. However I felt very sick and tired of being stuck in the traffic jam on the highway, people do not show up for appointments, misconception from other people who think that I am only after their money, constantly worrying about running out of prospects to meet in order to close more sales for my business. It was during this time, I saw my good friends who are full time online entrepreneurs, have been making good money just by Advertising and Marketing Online. I wondered, if they can make money using simple tools such as Facebook Chat, why not me? It shouldn\'t be that difficult. I am sure I can learn the art of Facebook Chat and be very good at it. Thus, I decided to take a leap of faith to learn about Internet Marketing to make my dream of Living N Earning anywhere and anytime to come true.","c36245a.png"," <p><br>I thought to myself, in the future, I would like to have a business which not only can bring financial freedom to me, but also allows me to have the opportunity to learn and grow to become a better person to my love ones, as well as to serve and empower ladies in the community. I did not expect this little seed planted in my heart many years ago to come true in 2013 when the Ladies Rock Online was formed.    </p>\n\n <p>I love to dream. Since young, <strong>I dreamt to have a business which would give me freedom in terms of making money and time.</strong> I reckon my dad has played a major role in cultivating the  entrepreneurship spirit and lifelong learning attitude in my life. I 